@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

' Components
component "Data Sources" as DataSources
component "BigQuery" as BigQuery
component "BigQuery ML" as BQML
component "Kubeflow Pipelines" as KFP
component "Vertex AI" as VertexAI
component "Cloud Storage" as GCS
component "AI Platform Prediction" as AIPlatform
component "Custom ScaNN Service" as ScaNN
component "Google Ads API" as GoogleAds
component "Data Studio" as DataStudio

' Data flow
DataSources --> BigQuery : Import Data
BigQuery --> BQML : Train Models
BQML --> KFP : Orchestrate ML Workflows
KFP --> VertexAI : Deploy Models
KFP --> GCS : Store Artifacts
KFP --> AIPlatform : Deploy Models
KFP --> ScaNN : Build Index
AIPlatform --> GoogleAds : Activate Predictions
VertexAI --> GoogleAds : Activate Predictions
BigQuery --> DataStudio : Visualize Results

' Control flow
KFP -[#red]-> BQML : Trigger Training
KFP -[#red]-> GCS : Manage Artifacts
KFP -[#red]-> AIPlatform : Manage Deployments
KFP -[#red]-> VertexAI : Manage Deployments
KFP -[#red]-> ScaNN : Trigger Index Build

' Notes
note right of BQML
  - Matrix Factorization
  - Propensity Models
  - LTV Prediction
  - Time Series Forecasting
end note

note right of KFP
  Orchestrates:
  - Data Preparation
  - Model Training
  - Evaluation
  - Deployment
end note

note right of ScaNN
  Real-time 
  Item-to-Item 
  Recommendations
end note

@enduml